## Workflow for Features

```
implementer → researcher
          ↓
      ui-designer (always — skips gate if no UI work)
          ↓ GATE: approve mockups
      designer
          ↓ GATE: approve design
      planner → plan-reviewer
          ↓ GATE: approve plan
{{#if_flag "has_backend" profile}}      backend-developer
          ↓ (commits: models → service → handler)
{{/if_flag}}{{#if_flag "has_infra" profile}}      infra-developer (always — self-assesses)
          ↓
{{/if_flag}}{{#if_flag "has_frontend" profile}}      frontend-developer
          ↓ (commits: service → components → pages)
{{/if_flag}}      tester → reviewer (2 passes) → cleaner → formatter
          ↓ GATE: final commit approval
```

